  characterName: Takano Saki
  description: A short and plump girl with a strong will and a heart of gold. In
    spite of her size, she never holds herself back from achieving big things. The
    harmony of the classroom amongst all the students in her class is of utmost importance,
    so she always delivers a big smile to everyone she talks to. She's destined for
    student council president!
